    <string name="permission_location_needs_settings">Location is blocked. Open settings and enable precise location for Pilgrim to continue.</string>

    <string name="battery_exemption_title">A word about sleep</string>
    <string name="battery_exemption_body">Android may pause recording when the screen is off. Ask your phone to let Pilgrim keep listening to location on long walks.</string>
    <string name="battery_exemption_body_samsung">Samsung phones can be especially strict. After this prompt, find Pilgrim in Settings → Battery → Background usage limits → Sleeping apps, and remove it.</string>
    <string name="battery_exemption_body_xiaomi">Xiaomi\'s MIUI can kill background services aggressively. After this prompt, also enable AutoStart for Pilgrim in Security → Permissions → Autostart.</string>
